1177
01:52:08,622 --> 01:52:11,321
You don't fast, take communion
or go to confession.

1178
01:52:11,421 --> 01:52:15,554
If I lit candles and all,
would things be different?

1179
01:52:15,720 --> 01:52:18,520
Maybe it's not too late to start?

1180
01:52:19,153 --> 01:52:21,386
Would I get my wife
back from the dead?

1181
01:52:21,519 --> 01:52:23,352
And my house?

1182
01:52:23,752 --> 01:52:25,485
Or is it too late?

1183
01:52:26,185 --> 01:52:27,418
I don't know.

1184
01:52:27,551 --> 01:52:29,951
Our Lord moves in mysterious ways.

1185
01:52:30,051 --> 01:52:31,817
You don't know?

1186
01:52:31,917 --> 01:52:35,583
Then why do you call me
to confession?

1187
01:52:37,283 --> 01:52:38,982
What do you know then?

1188
01:52:39,149 --> 01:52:41,215
- Want some?
- No.

1189
01:52:45,814 --> 01:52:48,647
"Can you pull in Leviathan
with a fishhook

1190
01:52:49,380 --> 01:52:52,080
