1191
01:52:52,712 --> 01:52:55,279
"Will it keep begging you for mercy?

1192
01:52:55,379 --> 01:52:58,711
"Will it speak to you
with gentle words?

1193
01:52:59,245 --> 01:53:01,678
"Nothing on earth is its equal.

1194
01:53:02,377 --> 01:53:04,510
"It is king over all that are proud."

1195
01:53:04,610 --> 01:53:06,109
Father Vasily...

1196
01:53:07,309 --> 01:53:09,842
I'm talking to you
as a regular person.

1197
01:53:09,976 --> 01:53:12,075
Why the fucking riddles?

1198
01:53:12,175 --> 01:53:13,708
What for?

1199
01:53:13,841 --> 01:53:16,741
Have you heard of a man called Job?

1200
01:53:17,174 --> 01:53:20,673
Like you, he was preoccupied
with the meaning of life.

1201
01:53:20,806 --> 01:53:23,506
"Why?" he asked.
"Why me of all people?"

1202
01:53:23,639 --> 01:53:26,772
He worried so much
he became covered with scabs.

1203
01:53:26,872 --> 01:53:30,671
His wife tried to talk some sense
into him; his friends told him

1204
01:53:31,138 --> 01:53:32,804
to not evoke God's anger.

1205
01:53:32,904 --> 01:53:36,770
But he kept kicking up dust
and sprinkling ash on his head.

1206
01:53:36,836 --> 01:53:39,736
Then the Lord relented

1207
01:53:39,869 --> 01:53:41,335
and appeared to him

1208
01:53:41,469 --> 01:53:43,469
in the form of a hurricane

1209
01:53:43,601 --> 01:53:46,734
and explained everything to him
in pictures.

1210
01:53:46,901 --> 01:53:48,034
And?

1211
01:53:48,534 --> 01:53:50,767
Job resigned himself to his fate

1212
01:53:50,867 --> 01:53:53,333
and lived to be 140.

1213
01:53:53,433 --> 01:53:57,466
Got to see 4 generations
of his family

1214
01:53:58,098 --> 01:54:00,198
and died old

1215
01:54:00,331 --> 01:54:01,497
and content.

1216
01:54:01,631 --> 01:54:03,164
Is that a fairy tale?

1217
01:54:06,730 --> 01:54:07,996
No,

1218
01:54:08,396 --> 01:54:10,429
it's in the Bible.

1219
01:54:10,563 --> 01:54:13,695
Let me help you carry that.
Come on.

1220
01:54:26,359 --> 01:54:27,592
Thanks.

1221
01:54:29,525 --> 01:54:33,258
