1270
01:58:46,969 --> 01:58:48,303
Next,

1271
01:58:49,435 --> 01:58:53,468
we have testimony
from Angela Polivanova

1272
01:58:54,668 --> 01:58:58,001
and her husband, Pasha Polivanov

1273
01:58:58,800 --> 01:59:02,232
to the effect that a few days
prior to the murder,

1274
01:59:02,366 --> 01:59:04,132
while at a picnic,

1275
01:59:04,266 --> 01:59:06,731
you had a fight with your wife

1276
01:59:06,899 --> 01:59:09,265
and her lover in front of witnesses.

1277
01:59:09,398 --> 01:59:11,798
after you caught them having sex.

1278
01:59:11,964 --> 01:59:14,163
You beat up the lover,

1279
01:59:14,297 --> 01:59:15,663
a man called Dmitri,

1280
01:59:16,197 --> 01:59:18,063
whose identity
is currently being established,

1281
01:59:18,163 --> 01:59:22,195
then hit your wife, and afterwards
threatened to kill them both.

1282
01:59:22,828 --> 01:59:24,961
This testimony was confirmed

1283
01:59:26,261 --> 01:59:28,360
by Ivan Stepanych Degtyaryev,

1284
01:59:29,094 --> 01:59:31,760
Lieutenant Colonel
of the traffic police,

1285
01:59:31,926 --> 01:59:35,159
who was also present.

1286
01:59:36,192 --> 01:59:39,524
In addition,
the suspected murder weapon,

1287
01:59:39,624 --> 01:59:43,324
a hammer with the shape matching
that of the Victim's head wound,

1288
01:59:44,191 --> 01:59:48,790
