on your property.

1289
01:59:48,922 --> 01:59:50,922
It has been taken for testing.

1290
01:59:51,389 --> 01:59:54,255
Would you like to comment
on any of this?

1291
01:59:55,288 --> 01:59:58,320
Personally, I would advise you

1292
01:59:59,020 --> 02:00:00,820
to write a full confession.

1293
02:00:00,920 --> 02:00:03,186
We have more than enough evidence.

1294
02:00:03,286 --> 02:00:06,052
A confession may reduce the sentence.

1295
02:00:06,552 --> 02:00:08,752
Pursuant to Article 105 Part 1,

1296
02:00:09,252 --> 02:00:12,384
you'll get up to 15 years

1297
02:00:12,484 --> 02:00:14,950
unless there are
aggravating circumstances,

1298
02:00:15,050 --> 02:00:18,150
in which case,
it'll be up to 20 years.

1299
02:00:21,183 --> 02:00:22,549
Right...

1300
02:00:23,482 --> 02:00:26,381
In any case,
we're detaining you for 48 hours

1301
02:00:26,481 --> 02:00:28,481
as a murder suspect.

1302
02:00:29,481 --> 02:00:32,647
I'll petition the court
for a warrant for your arrest

1303
02:00:32,780 --> 02:00:37,845
as a flight risk and as someone
who might impede the investigation.

1304
02:00:44,744 --> 02:00:45,944
Also...

1305
02:00:46,510 --> 02:00:49,409
you have the right to a lawyer.

1306
02:00:49,543 --> 02:00:51,909
If you don't have a lawyer,

1307
02:00:52,009 --> 02:00:54,075
the state will appoint one for you.

1308
02:00:54,975 --> 02:00:56,641
Do you understand?

1309
02:00:59,941 --> 02:01:02,107
