Listen...

1314
02:02:05,760 --> 02:02:09,192
My son's left all alone.

1315
02:02:10,459 --> 02:02:11,891
We've got no relatives.

1316
02:02:12,025 --> 02:02:13,425
Don't shit yourself.

1317
02:02:14,125 --> 02:02:16,290
The state will take care of him.

1318
02:03:12,678 --> 02:03:15,378
Roma, open up.
It's Angela and Pasha.

1319
02:03:15,511 --> 02:03:17,077
Are you alone?

1320
02:03:17,177 --> 02:03:18,344
Yes, it's just us.

1321
02:03:24,276 --> 02:03:25,743
How are you?

1322
02:03:26,243 --> 02:03:27,575
I'm all right.

1323
02:03:28,242 --> 02:03:31,341
Why didn't you call me
when they took your dad?

1324
02:03:32,274 --> 02:03:34,174
I don't have your number.

1325
02:03:36,907 --> 02:03:39,106
How long have you
been here alone?

1326
02:03:39,240 --> 02:03:40,440
I don't know.

1327
02:03:41,306 --> 02:03:43,372
5 days, I think.

1328
02:03:44,705 --> 02:03:45,905
Roma...

1329
02:03:47,338 --> 02:03:49,338
A lawyer called.

1330
02:03:50,437 --> 02:03:53,137
Your dad was accused
of murdering Lilya.

1331
02:03:54,037 --> 02:03:58,136
He'll be in jail till the trial.
Then, they'll take him to prison.

1332
02:03:59,368 --> 02:04:01,135
They have proof.

1333
02:04:01,235 --> 02:04:02,601
That's not true.

1334
02:04:02,701 --> 02:04:04,634
Why would I lie to you?

1335
02:04:06,900 --> 02:04:10,166
Why didn't he call me?
They must let him call me.

1336
02:04:10,266 --> 02:04:11,866
Look, Roma,

1337
02:04:12,665 --> 02:04:15,865
the lawyer said that
if there's no one to take care of you,

1338
02:04:15,965 --> 02:04:17,664
they'll put you in an orphanage.

1339
02:04:18,498 --> 02:04:20,597
I can take care of myself.

1340
02:04:20,697 --> 02:04:23,730
By law, until you turn 18,

1341
02:04:23,863 --> 02:04:27,196
you must live
in an orphanage or with a guardian.

1342
02:04:28,129 --> 02:04:30,329
Pasha and I talked it over...

1343
02:04:30,961 --> 02:04:33,261
We'd like to be your guardians.

1344
02:04:33,361 --> 02:04:35,260
You've got no one else, right?

1345
02:04:41,326 --> 02:04:42,726
Is it because of the money?

1346
02:04:43,326 --> 02:04:44,658
What money?

1347
02:04:44,758 --> 02:04:46,458
Won't you get paid for it?

1348
02:04:46,558 --> 02:04:48,358
How should I know?

1349
02:04:49,857 --> 02:04:53,324
But if you agree,
I'll definitely find out.

1350
02:04:53,457 --> 02:04:56,423
I guess the state
would probably help out,

1351
02:04:57,123 --> 02:04:59,155
but that's not why we're offering.

1352
02:04:59,722 --> 02:05:01,355
Why then?

1353
02:05:02,522 --> 02:05:03,888
I don't know.

1354
02:05:05,221 --> 02:05:06,521
You're like...

1355
02:05:07,221 --> 02:05:08,753
family to us.

1356
02:05:09,453 --> 02:05:11,086
Your mum and I were friends.

1357
02:05:11,220 --> 02:05:14,252
You were little when she died.

1358
02:05:15,585 --> 02:05:19,684
I went to school with your parents.
And Lilya. She was a bit younger.

1359
02:05:31,648 --> 02:05:33,282
I'll step out for a smoke.

1360
02:07:33,122 --> 02:07:36,189
Pribrezhny Town Court
has ruled as follows:

1361
02:07:36,321 --> 02:07:39,921
The Panel of Judges,

1362
02:07:40,021 --> 02:07:45,587
presided over by Mrs Tarasova,
examined Mr Sergeyev's petition

1363
02:07:45,687 --> 02:07:48,619
to appeal the ruling
on case No. 06-18.

1364
02:07:48,752 --> 02:07:52,518
In the presence of Mr Sergeyev,
the court has determined that:

1365
02:07:52,651 --> 02:07:55,484
Mr Sergeyev,
who has no previous convictions,

1366
02:07:55,617 --> 02:07:58,984
is convicted in accordance
with Article 105 of the Criminal Code

1367
02:07:59,084 --> 02:08:02,649
and sentenced to 15 years
in a maximum-security penitentiary.

1368
02:08:02,783 --> 02:08:05,549
The ruling also addressed
evidence in the case:

1369
02:08:05,649 --> 02:08:10,281
Mr Sergeyev was convicted
of premeditated murder of his wife.

1370
02:08:10,381 --> 02:08:14,080
The circumstances of the crime
are outlined in the ruling.

1371
02:08:14,180 --> 02:08:16,713
Mr Sergeyev refused
to confess to the crime.

1372
02:08:16,846 --> 02:08:21,279
He filed an appeal requesting
that the ruling be repealed.

1373
02:08:21,379 --> 02:08:25,478
Mr Sergeyev claims that his guilt
in the case was not proven.

1374
02:08:25,611 --> 02:08:30,543
The court considers the ruling
not subject to repeal.

1375
02:08:30,977 --> 02:08:34,176
All circumstances
were thoroughly examined by the court

1376
02:08:34,309 --> 02:08:36,508
and all evidence
given due consideration.

1377
02:08:36,642 --> 02:08:40,175
The defendant's claim of innocence
was reviewed by the court

1378
02:08:40,307 --> 02:08:41,507
and soundly rejected.

1379
02:09:03,003 --> 02:09:04,302
Hello?

1380
02:09:08,769 --> 02:09:10,401
15 years?

1381
02:09:10,535 --> 02:09:12,301
Well, thank God.

1382
02:09:12,434 --> 02:09:15,067
That'll teach him to know his place.

1383
02:09:16,467 --> 02:09:18,266
Yeah, later.

1384
02:09:24,198 --> 02:09:25,631
One more.

1385
02:09:45,193 --> 02:09:50,360
We probably don't even realise yet
what is really happening.

1386
02:09:51,126 --> 02:09:53,492
We are reawakening

1387
02:09:54,292 --> 02:09:56,725
the soul of the Russian people.

1388
02:09:57,758 --> 02:10:02,623
As the Great Prince
St. Alexander Nevsky

1389
02:10:02,757 --> 02:10:05,056
wonderfully put it:

1390
02:10:05,156 --> 02:10:08,856
"God dwells not in strength,
but in truth."

1391
02:10:08,956 --> 02:10:12,721
And he was right:
not with strength, but with love;

1392
02:10:12,821 --> 02:10:14,554
not with cunning,

1393
02:10:14,654 --> 02:10:16,920
but with the Lord's wisdom;

1394
02:10:17,020 --> 02:10:20,186
not with anger and hatred,
but with bravery

1395
02:10:20,319 --> 02:10:24,719
have we overcome the many enemies
of our faith and our Motherland.

1396
02:10:25,818 --> 02:10:29,051
But the most important thing today

1397
02:10:29,884 --> 02:10:32,251
is that we must

1398
02:10:32,383 --> 02:10:34,450
uphold the Orthodox faith

1399
02:10:34,550 --> 02:10:36,750
and always speak truthfully.

1400
02:10:37,249 --> 02:10:38,782
Truth

1401
02:10:38,915 --> 02:10:41,381
is God's legacy.

1402
02:10:41,481 --> 02:10:46,180
Truth reflects the world
as it really is, without distortion.

1403
02:10:46,914 --> 02:10:52,046
But only he who knows God's truth
can find truth.

1404
02:10:52,146 --> 02:10:55,945
And God's truth
is Christ Himself.

1405
02:10:56,078 --> 02:10:58,578
This is why, when Apostle Paul said,

1406
02:10:58,678 --> 02:11:02,110
"I no longer live,
but Christ lives in me"

1407
02:11:03,310 --> 02:11:07,143
he meant that when a man
lets Christ into his soul -

1408
02:11:07,843 --> 02:11:10,275
in other words,
begins to think like Christ,

1409
02:11:10,375 --> 02:11:12,042
see like Christ

1410
02:11:12,142 --> 02:11:15,374
and act like the Lord commanded -

1411
02:11:15,474 --> 02:11:19,807
only then does this man
possess truth.

1412
02:11:20,506 --> 02:11:23,072
And that means he can regard events

1413
02:11:23,972 --> 02:11:26,272
and see their true meaning

1414
02:11:26,372 --> 02:11:29,671
and tell good from evil.

1415
02:11:29,804 --> 02:11:33,170
And that is the essence of truth.

1416
02:11:33,270 --> 02:11:37,336
When people destroy crosses,

1417
02:11:37,403 --> 02:11:41,268
break icons, defile the Crucifix

1418
02:11:42,202 --> 02:11:45,201
and blaspheme by calling
demonic rites a prayer,

1419
02:11:45,335 --> 02:11:48,167
when people try to convince others

1420
02:11:48,300 --> 02:11:51,266
that they do this
out of good intentions,

1421
02:11:51,366 --> 02:11:53,099
they are passing off lies

1422
02:11:53,233 --> 02:11:55,565
as the truth.

1423
02:11:55,665 --> 02:11:57,432
How can one

1424
02:11:57,565 --> 02:12:01,398
preach freedom
while destroying the foundations

1425
02:12:01,498 --> 02:12:03,564
of morality?

1426
02:12:03,664 --> 02:12:07,463
Freedom is finding God's truth.

1427
02:12:07,596 --> 02:12:10,262
The Bible teaches us this.

1428
02:12:10,396 --> 02:12:14,428
Know God's truth,
and it shall set you free.

1429
02:12:16,361 --> 02:12:20,394
Only man who knows God's truth,
who lives by it,

1430
02:12:20,494 --> 02:12:22,459
who defends it -

1431
02:12:22,559 --> 02:12:25,093
only that man is truly free.

1432
02:12:26,326 --> 02:12:30,791
My beloved brothers and sisters
in Christ!

1433
02:12:30,925 --> 02:12:36,390
The world today is constantly
changing its reference points.

1434
02:12:37,024 --> 02:12:39,523
True values

1435
02:12:40,056 --> 02:12:42,255
are being replaced with false ones.

1436
02:12:42,389 --> 02:12:45,622
But even in this world,

1437
02:12:46,554 --> 02:12:50,221
our path remains unchanged:
it leads to Christ.

1438
02:12:50,353 --> 02:12:54,420
We know that the Church
will protect and guide us

1439
02:12:54,553 --> 02:12:58,185
but the Church consists
of you and me.

1440
02:12:58,285 --> 02:12:59,819
God is with us.

1441
02:12:59,919 --> 02:13:02,718
Truth is with us.
The Lord's love is with us...

1442
02:13:04,318 --> 02:13:06,550
God sees everything, son.

1443
02:13:06,650 --> 02:13:11,482
And in defending our faith, we will
not liken ourselves to our enemies

1444
02:13:11,582 --> 02:13:13,116
but just as Christ

1445
02:13:13,249 --> 02:13:17,215
shed light on the truth
and unmasked the lies with one word,

1446
02:13:17,348 --> 02:13:20,880
so will we,
enlightened by the Church,

1447
02:13:21,414 --> 02:13:24,146
the World of God and saintly prayer

1448
02:13:24,246 --> 02:13:26,413
defend the Orthodox faith.

1449
02:13:27,713 --> 02:13:30,045
I'm so glad
that you're pleased, sir.

1450
02:13:30,145 --> 02:13:32,344
Thanks a lot. We try.

1451
02:13:36,111 --> 02:13:39,510
It's not quite finished yet,
but it will be soon.

1452
02:13:40,276 --> 02:13:44,342
We'll do some landscaping,
maybe build a refectory.

1453
02:13:44,442 --> 02:13:47,341
As soon as it's all finished,
I'll call you right away.

1454
02:13:48,341 --> 02:13:51,307
- I have every faith in you.
- Thank you so much.

1455
02:13:52,007 --> 02:13:53,373
Where's my family?

1456
02:13:53,507 --> 02:13:55,807
Come on, sweetie, get in the car.

